WEBVTT

00:00:28.525 --> 00:00:32.262
Kao što mu njegov štitonoša
Sančo Pansa objašnjava iznova i iznova,

00:00:32.702 --> 00:00:34.386
to nisu džinovi:

00:00:34.386 --> 00:00:36.790
to su samo vetrenjače.

00:00:36.790 --> 00:00:38.471
Don Kihot je odlučan,

00:00:38.483 --> 00:00:40.128
ali njegovo oštro koplje

00:00:40.128 --> 00:00:42.807
je uskoro uhvaćeno u njihovim jedrima.

00:00:42.807 --> 00:00:44.296
Nikad obeshrabren,

00:00:44.296 --> 00:00:46.398
vitez ponosno stoji

00:00:46.398 --> 00:00:49.462
i postaje čak i ubeđeniji u svoju misiju.

00:00:50.546 --> 00:00:55.229
Ova epizoda sadrži
sve što volimo kod Don Kihota:

00:00:55.362 --> 00:00:58.868
epsku, nelogičnu priču s dušom

00:00:58.868 --> 00:01:00.236
o Alonsu Kihanu